430
00:32:35,909 --> 00:32:38,955
dan algojo publiknya,

431
00:32:38,956 --> 00:32:41,862
George Maledon.

432
00:32:43,857 --> 00:32:46,264
{\an8}HAKIM ISAAC C. PARKER

433
00:32:44,618 --> 00:32:48,360
{\an5}Mereka adalah bajingan
